keyMappings:
# Scrolling
map j scrollDown count=4
map k scrollUp count=4

map J scrollDown count=16
map K scrollUp count=16
unmap <c-e>
unmap <c-y>

# Navigation
# TODO: figure out shift-tab
#map <shift><tab> previousTab
#map <tab> nextTab

map < previousTab
map > nextTab
map <a->> moveTabRight
map <a-<> moveTabLeft
unmap <<
unmap >>

# Marks
map m Marks.activateGotoMode
map M Marks.activateCreateMode
unmap `

# Tab Manipulation
map d removeTab
map u restoreTab

#map t createTab chrome-extension://dbepggeogbaibhgnhhndojpepiihcmeb/pages/options.html

# Vomnibar
map o Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
unmap O
map b Vomnibar.activateBookmarksInNewTab
unmap B
map s Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=g
map <c-k> Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=g
map <c-l> Vomnibar.activateEditUrlInNewTab

# Miscellaneous
map Y copyCurrentUrl
map R reload hard

# q to escape
#mapkey q <c-[>
